data.title: The Armoury
data.meta_description: The Armoury was born from our passion for classic styling and interest in the unique stories behind well-crafted mens products.
data.text:
A wedding is undoubtedly one of lifes most important occasions, and a wedding suit one of the most special pieces in any mans wardrobe. Our team are expertly trained to create something perfect down to the last detail.

Every garment that comes through our shops is measured for quality control. We work with a wide range of tailors and artisans, so we inevitably have a varying assortment of fits and styles.

Our partnership with Ascot Chang spans the better part of a decade, which gives us the ability to offer many of our Dayware products in a range of fabrics, from cottons and linens to wool based for the winter.
